  "pageTitle": "面向现代资源回收设施的两套系统",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"products-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">产品线</p>\n        <h1 id=\"products-title\">面向现代资源回收设施的两套系统</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">比较AI可回收塑料光学分拣系统与建筑、装饰、拆除和大件废弃物项目中的集成C&D废弃物回收管线。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section product-family-intro\" id=\"product-comparison\" aria-labelledby=\"product-families-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">独立解族</p>\n        <h2 id=\"product-families-title\">这是两条不同的项目路径，而不是同一个目录的两种变体</h2>\n        <p>其中一个产品系列专为高价值塑料识别和光学分拣而建。另一台则用于重型破碎、筛选以及C&D和大件废弃物项目中的资源利用。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"product-family-band product-family-ai\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-family-title\">\n        <div class=\"product-family-inner\">\n          <picture class=\"product-family-media\">\n            <img src=\"/assets/images/super-sorting.jpg\" alt=\"WEI LAN 配备模块化分拣设备的超光学分拣系统配置\">\n          </picture>\n          <div class=\"product-family-content\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">超级光学分拣系统</p>\n            <h2 id=\"ai-family-title\">AI 可回收塑料光学分拣中心</h2>\n            <p>模块化分拣模块可按材质和颜色识别并区分PET瓶、HDPE瓶、PP和混合塑料。</p>\n            <div class=\"product-family-chips\" aria-label=\"典型材料\">\n              <span>PET瓶</span>\n              <span>HDPE瓶</span>\n              <span>PP塑料</span>\n              <span>混合可回收物</span>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"product-family-metrics\" aria-label=\"AI光学分选亮点\">\n              <div>\n                <dt>0.6-2 t/h</dt>\n                <dd>吞吐量范围</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt>5-10</dt>\n                <dd>物料类别</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt>滑架模块</dt>\n                <dd>更快的安装</dd>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n            <p class=\"product-action-strip\"><a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/products/ai-optical-sorting\" aria-label=\"查看AI光学分拣系统 详情\">查看详情</a></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"product-family-band product-family-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"industrial-family-title\">\n        <div class=\"product-family-inner\">\n          <div class=\"product-family-content\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">建筑与大件废弃物处理线</p>\n            <h2 id=\"industrial-family-title\">综合C&D废弃物处理与资源利用线路</h2>\n            <p>Lion One一体化破碎与筛选站结合了进料、破碎、筛分、磁选、气流分离和打包设备。</p>\n            <div class=\"product-engineering-brief\">\n              <ol class=\"product-process-chain\" aria-label=\"核心C&D 废弃物处理流程\">\n                <li>给料</li>\n                <li>破碎</li>\n                <li>筛分</li>\n                <li>磁分离</li>\n                <li>气流分离</li>\n                <li>打包</li>\n              </ol>\n              <dl class=\"product-line-specs\" aria-label=\"建筑废弃线亮点\">\n                <div>\n                  <dt>容量范围</dt>\n                  <dd>20-70 t/h</dd>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <dt>单机占地面积</dt>\n                  <dd>35 m<sup>2</sup></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <dt>可调节破碎尺寸</dt>\n                  <dd>液压驱动</dd>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"product-action-strip\">\n              <a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/products/construction-waste-recycling-line\" aria-label=\"查看建筑废弃管线规范\">查看详情</a>\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <picture class=\"product-family-media\">\n            <img src=\"/assets/images/lion-mark1.jpg\" alt=\"WEI LAN建筑和装饰废料的综合破碎与筛分站\">\n          </picture>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"contact-section\" aria-labelledby=\"products-inquiry-title\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">项目探究</p>\n          <h2 id=\"products-inquiry-title\">发送你的物资和容量需求</h2>\n          <p>分享你正在评估的废弃物流、目标吞吐量、场地限制和项目阶段。WEI LAN可以推荐合适的产品线，并准备更有针对性的提案讨论。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"about-contact-panel compact-contact-panel\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求产品提案</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/solutions\">复习解决方案路径</a>\n          <p>销售热线：+86 137 8001 2268 / +86 180 6737 7770</p>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" id=\"specs\" aria-labelledby=\"specs-title\" hidden>\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">规格</p>\n          <h2 id=\"specs-title\">核心产品参数</h2>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-ai\" aria-labelledby=\"spec-group-ai\">\n          <header class=\"spec-group-head\">\n            <span class=\"spec-group-tag\">超光学分拣</span>\n            <h3 id=\"spec-group-ai\">GL01V系列</h3>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"spec-card-grid\">\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-1\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-01</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V1-5</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">迷你版</p>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <i></i><i></i>\n                </span>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:35%\">\n                  <dt>容量</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.6&ndash;0.8<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:55%\">\n                  <dt>动力</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">30<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:38%\">\n                  <dt>覆盖范围</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">24<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安装占地 ·8 × 3 m版面 ·3 m 净空高度</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:50%\">\n                  <dt>分选范围</dt>\n                  <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">5<small>物料类型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分选范围：透明PET·彩色PET·HDPE ·PP ·混合塑料\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\">PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-2\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-02</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V2-9</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">标准</p>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <i></i><i></i>\n                </span>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:58%\">\n                  <dt>容量</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.8&ndash;1.2<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:78%\">\n                  <dt>动力</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">45<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                  <dt>覆盖范围</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">36<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安装占地 ·12 × 3 m版面 ·6 m 净空高度</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:90%\">\n                  <dt>分选范围</dt>\n                  <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">9<small>物料类型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分选范围：透明PET·绿色PET ·蓝色PET ·混色PET·白色HDPE·彩色HDPE·PP ·混合塑料·拒绝\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\">PET颜色·HDPE ·PP ·混合·拒绝</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-3\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-03</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V3-10</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">而且</p>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <i></i><i></i>\n                </span>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:95%\">\n                  <dt>容量</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">1.5&ndash;2<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                  <dt>动力</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">53<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                  <dt>覆盖范围</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">51<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安装占地 ·17 × 3 m版面 ·6 m 净空高度</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                  <dt>分选范围</dt>\n                  <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">10<small>物料类型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分选范围：透明PET·绿色PET ·蓝色PET ·混色PET·白色HDPE·彩色HDPE·PP ·PE ·混合塑料·拒绝\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\">PET颜色·HDPE ·PP ·PE ·混合·拒绝</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"spec-group-cdw\">\n          <header class=\"spec-group-head\">\n            <span class=\"spec-group-tag\">C&D 废弃物管线</span>\n            <h3 id=\"spec-group-cdw\">Lion One综合车站</h3>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-wide\">\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-industrial\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">L1</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">Lion One</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">综合破碎与筛分站</p>\n                </div>\n                <dl class=\"spec-card-plate\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div><dt>MFG</dt><dd>WEI&nbsp;LAN</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>类型</dt><dd>移动&nbsp;站</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>等级</dt><dd>重型&nbsp;</dd></div>\n                </dl>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics spec-metrics-wide\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>容量</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">20&ndash;70</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">t/h</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>进给尺寸</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">200</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">mm</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>覆盖范围</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">35</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">m<sup>2</sup> · 11.7 × 3 × 3.1 m</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>驱动</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">100<small>%</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">全液压</span></dd>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n              <footer class=\"spec-card-foot\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-mark\">WEI LAN</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>宁波，中国</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>集成移动站</span>\n              </footer>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
